{"tid":1837340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"順利邨突發火魔法  大頭緑衣罰企","createTime":"2020-01-23T14:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T01:00:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":501,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"a78d17d9c79ea045a7efd6769f55b22d2272ace1","tid":1837340,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200123/photo/bkn-20200123215548569-0123_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200123223403\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200123215548569-0123_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200123223403&h=b1ff7bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民發起於今晚(23日)8時許，到秀茂坪順利邨進行突發行動，約10名示威者參加，他們在順利商場對開叫號。約一小時後，有警車駛經利安道，有示威者隨即縱火，及掟出馬路，有市民見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n消防接報到場，迅速開喉射水將火救熄，示威者亦陸續散去。其後，一批防暴警到場，在附近行人天橋搜索示威者，並截查可疑人。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200123/mobile/bkn-20200123215548569-0123_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a519fecb8c261d3fac1fd21fa1c388056457458f","tid":1837340,"uid":288670,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"拎走左手足個人資料"},{"pid":"66c956d02534866aab92aa7b5d512de9a0826250","tid":1837340,"uid":126621,"like":153,"dislike":2,"score":151,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"good job<br />\n讓綠曱甴長期暴露係空氣當中<br />\n好快會自然死亡無可疑"},{"pid":"3b9337c203faf2648e8b539bc4772418ddc20433","tid":1837340,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"［行動］文宣向有意到港醫病嘅武漢肺炎病人，引導佢地搵香港警署求助<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837289</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eade4d8f4ccd632a0d8a8fbfd8e5be6a396dc4c3","tid":1837340,"uid":45213,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"幫手消毒姐"},{"pid":"c5b4070c706937d2fb5f027ceb752c27dbc56efe","tid":1837340,"uid":184